###
    TMUX GENERAL SHORTCUTS
    by luca
###

# GENERAL
<Prefix> :      open command line
<Prefix> ,      rename window 

# SWITCH WINDOW
<Prefix> n      switch to next window
<Prefix> p      switch to previous window 
<Prefix> [x]    switch to window by number


# SWITCH PANES
<Prefix> l      switch to right pane
<Prefix> h      switch to left pane
<Prefix> j      switch to bottom pane
<Prefix> k      switch to top pane
<Prefix> q [x]  switch to pane by number

# PANE RESIZING
<Prefix> CTRL l  resize pane to the right
<Prefix> CTRL h  resize pane to the left
<Prefix> CTRL j  resize pane to the bottom
<Prefix> CTRL k  resize pane to the top
<Prefix> z       resize pane to fullscreen

# CREATE
<Prefix> w  create new window
<Prefix> t  create vertical split 
<Prefix> -  create horizontal split

# DELETE
<Prefix> x  delete window or pane 
